### Account Service API Examples

# Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8009
@token = your-jwt-token-here
@internalToken = your-internal-secret-token-here

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Root Endpoint
GET {{baseUrl}}/

### Create Account
POST {{baseUrl}}/accounts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "My Checking Account",
  "type": "checking",
  "currency": "USD",
  "balance": 1000.00,
  "description": "Primary checking account"
}

### List Accounts
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### List Accounts (including archived)
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts?include_archived=true
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Account by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update Account
PUT {{baseUrl}}/accounts/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Account Name",
  "description": "Updated description"
}

### Archive Account
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/accounts/1/archive
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Account Summary
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts/1/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Account Transactions
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts/1/transactions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Account Transactions with Pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts/1/transactions?limit=50&offset=0
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update Account Balance
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/accounts/1/balance?balance=1500.00
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Internal: Validate Account
GET {{baseUrl}}/internal/accounts/1/validate?user_id=1
X-Internal-Token: {{internalToken}}

### Internal: Get Account Details
GET {{baseUrl}}/internal/accounts/1?user_id=1
X-Internal-Token: {{internalToken}}
